# AudioFileStreamID

**Type Alias**

Defines an opaque data type that represents an audio file stream parser.

## Declaration

```swift
typealias AudioFileStreamID = OpaquePointer
```

## Data Types

- **AudioFileStreamPropertyID**: Uniquely identifies an audio file stream property.
